  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion

          -  Patients 65 years or older with RA diagnosed according to the ACR / EULAR 1987/2010
             criteria,

          -  disease duration 2 years or more,

          -  disease activity as measured by DAS28 &lt;5.1

        Exclusion

          -  Comorbidities, such as unstable coronary artery disease, uncontrolled cardiac
             arrhythmia, or uncontrolled high blood pressure, which prevents moderate to intense
             exercise.

          -  Joint surgery completed within 6 months prior to study entry.

          -  Ongoing training at moderate to high level 2 or more times per week
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
